			The
			_menuContribution_
			contribution has an ID value which allow to identify the
			contribution.
		
		
			_menuContribution_
			has an
			_locationURI_
			attribute which allows to
			define where in the user interface a
			command
			is displayed. This different attribute values are summarized in the
			following table.
		

		
